- **PUA P10-9-8-7 Parallel Topology** (permanent law): **CEO → P10 (strategy) → P9 (Tech Lead, writes Prompts) → P8 (owns it, internally spawns P7) → P7**. 10 iron rules: ① **P9 dispatches multiple P8s in true parallel** (multiple Agent calls in same message) ② **P8 internally spawns P7**, P9 does not manage sub-topology ③ P10 does not write Task Prompts or manage P8 ④ **P9 never writes code** (role confusion = below 3.5) ⑤ CEO overrides P10 ⑥ File-domain isolation, grep verify ⑦ Same message multi-Agent = true parallel (not sequential) ⑧ Verification closure: P9 runs commands, no empty verbal claims ⑨ **P9 does not self-decide L4 strategy** (sprint kickoff / priority / Wave merge / Phase order / sprint outcome = L4 requires P10 ratification; violation triggers L41 rule) ⑩ **When user uses emphasis keywords, must read workflow** (Harness/OODC/PUA P10-9-8-7/Superpower pipeline/nested-parallel = must Read `$CLAUDE_HOME/workflows/<corresponding MD>.md` verbatim, L42 rule, memory recall not accepted). **Full diagram + decision tree + nested parallel**: `$CLAUDE_HOME/workflows/pua-topology.md`.

